         <abstract>
            <p>A family of artificial boundary conditions for the linear advection diffusion equation with small viscosity is developed. Well-posedness for the associated initial boundary value problem is analyzed. The error produced by truncating the domain is estimated. Numerical results are presented.</p>
          </abstract>
